      "content": "i blew it all. everything. the company is gone, the investors are suing, and i'm staring at more debt than i could pay off in three lifetimes. i can't even think about going back home. the look on my parents faces... the shame is just too much. i feel like i've reached the end of the road and there's nowhere left to go.",
